      "content": "A regression in commit [`73daec6`](https://github.com/curl/curl/commit/73daec6620bf9983df89e8df3660bfa3b8fd501d) caused `Curl_secure_context()` to use the proxy's HTTPS scheme instead of the origin's scheme when forwarding through an HTTPS proxy, leaking Secure cookies to HTTP origins in cleartext. Fix in PR [#22024](https://github.com/curl/curl/pull/22024).\n\nClosed as \"Not Applicable\" as the regression was not present in any release, only `origin/master`",
